text: Mundys Mill is an unincorporated community in Clayton County, in the U.S. state of Georgia. ==History== The community was named after E. T. and R. W. Mundy, proprietors of a local gristmill. ==Education== Mundy's Mill High School is operated by the Clayton County School District. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Clayton County, Georgia
title: Mundys Mill, Georgia
